      "annotation": "STEP 7a: Filter VCF to retain only high-quality variants: QUAL >= 200, DP >= 10, AF >= 0.90. This removes low-confidence calls and retains fixed or near-fixed mutations consistent with clonal bacterial genomes.",
      "content_id": "toolshed.g2.bx.psu.edu/repos/devteam/vcffilter/vcffilter2/1.0.0_rc3+galaxy3",
